-- Sargent Discusses Art of Cooking Fish in new Book (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-07-29T12:54:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-29/sargent-discusses-art-of-cooking-fish-in-new-book-audio-.html
Ben Sargent, host of "Hook Line, and
Dinner" on the Cooking Channel, discusses his new book "The 
Catch: Sea-to-Tables Recipes, Stories & Secrets," and the art of
cooking fish. Sargent talks with Bloomberg's Kathleen Hays and 
Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 07:22
 